        "timestamp": "2019-06-17 10:11:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\ndo not change the copyright of existing files. you can put the copyrights only on new files you created and there is  justification for it.\n\nwhy did you upgraded the jetty version? is there a functionality you need from  the new version?",
