        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-17 10:21:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIs this https change indeed fixes the issues listed on the Wiki linked to the Jira 2268?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "5b415a184ef923a96ae28f741e2bc419723e5acc",
